Constructs a new ParaFact object.

Parameters:
pos - - the original position in the file.
path - - a valid path to the Unit containing the paragraph.
n - - the name of the assertion (can be an empty string).
v - - the fact.
Throws:
ErrorSyntax - - if n contains '/' or '@'.
ErrorSyntax - - if n is equal to "none", "iden", "univ", or "Int".
ErrorInternal - - if path==null, n==null, or v==null.
